reviewText: FARGO was the only enjoyable flick. The other two are not worth watching
Three funny movies on one DVD, just keep the popcorn coming! Great!
These were ordered to replace VHS tapes of the same movies all three movies are good watches and we will now get to see them more often.
Well, I love 2/3s of it.  I find Raising Arizona silly, but Fargo and especially the Full Monty are excellent movies imho.
Three of my favorite movies!!!!!!! So excited to find them in one set!
